Fixing On-Page SEO of the website

Fixing On-Page SEO contains things like title, meta description, image-alt text, broken links, 404 error page, multiple h1 tag in one page, duplicate title/description, dynamic URL, sparse content page (word count <500), etc.
Fixed all the possible solutions that we can do for improving the SEO health score.
Fixed, image-alt text error, title, meta description, broken links, dynamic URL, 404 error page, sparse content pages, contact information on all pages, connecting website with Google search console.
